summary: Marry Gabriella's twin of the Dark Brotherhood.
descriptionHtml:
[b]
Gabrielle[/b] is found at Dead Man's Drink in Falkreath. Not too far from the dark brotherhood's sanctuary.

Info/spec:
#1 She is marriable
#2 Non essential NPC (should die)
#3 She is leveled to your character (ranging from level 15 to 999)

Without disrupting the game quests and avoid rendering save files asunder. Closest thing we can have to the original is a clone, a replication. While it is not original. As in her. Only difference in this case of Gabriella, is that she is not dead.

To be bound together, now and forever.

(Textures and Meshes directories have been included to avoid a character appearance bug. That causes the head of the NPC to not match the body.)
author: Feralas
